race.comment: BLAZEN BOOTS (4) has a solid record over this course and distance with two wins and a second from four attempts and will be high on confidence following that last-start victory here. Gun hoop Thompson sticks in the saddle and should be going very close again. NORTHERN DECREE (8) put in a better performance placing here last time out and will have come on with that run in the locker. Looms as the main danger. YET HE MOVES (1) gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim and doesn't know how to out in a poor one. Definite top-three prospects. KEITEL (2) goes well for rider Franklin who has two wins from as many rides. Include with the claim.
